metadata.name: Hauberk Under Tempest
metadata.description:
Suspended on an organic tempest sofa, a metallic vest resembling protection in a spiritual battle, surrenders to reptilian poison.

1500labs displays a process of almost instant rarefaction from fashion luxury objects to enigmatic and mysterious forms. Ceaseless mutations that materialize in a variety of outcomes, the symbolic, the unexplained or the sublime.

Unique 1/1 NFT
Format: MP4
Duration: 26 seconds
Resolution: 2160 x 2160px
